(secondQuint)A Trial to Evaluate the Improvement in Lung Cancer Patients Receiving Radiation With or Without Brachytherapy.

 In patients with advanced NSCLC to compare the added benefit of High Dose Rate Intraluminal Brachytherapy (HDRIB) with External Beam Radiation (EBR).

 Benefit will be assessed by measuring the proportion of patients who achieve symptomatic improvement in lung cancer symptoms.

